metadata.name: Thailand Bouldering Competition2022
metadata.description: TBC2022 This picture was painted to promote a rock climbing competition in Thailand. that has been held for at least 15 years and this year is the year I have been working on nft art. To be a space to keep your own artwork to stay in the world forever, no matter where you go People will know that I made it. Even though I myself have died It made me like ETH platform and it was the first platform I knew. this piece of my work Therefore, the symbol ETH was used to be a part of this work. to tell the value that directly affects me and in addition to digital art images I also included the ETH symbol in the image as part of the mountaineering race route. that are used in real races in this race as well, every What I do is my inspiration. have fun thank you very much
